  <brief_title>Physical Activity in Patients After Aortic Valve Replacement (Valve-ex)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Regular Physical Activity on Exercise Capacity, Cardiac Remodeling and Endothelial Function in Patients After Aortic Valve Replacement</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Technische Universität München</agency>
