    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with severe valvular aortic stenosis and indication for valve replacement

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Coronary heart disease with indication for additional bypass surgery Leading
             insufficiency of the valve

          -  Age &lt; 65 or &gt; 75

          -  Diseases or conditions leading to additional risks during physical activity (e.g.
             diabetes, arthrosis, obstructive pulmonary disease)
      </textblock>
